              Do not go by the photo.  There are videos on youtube showing this thing.  When I first saw the photo (actually, on Gizmodo, I think, you can find my comments), I laughed heartily, saying, "No way that's going to work for fingertip gamers".  Then I saw the video.  Holy crap, this thing is awesome.  The complete customizability is what really makes it attractive.  Hell, it's perfect for fingertip gamers, claw grip gamers, palm grip gamers, and gamers who sit on their mouse.  It's so disturbingly awesome, I almost want two.<BR><BR>Problem is the expense... $130 for the wireless version?  G-damn.

              

              
              
            </div>
