        <tr>
          <td class="post-content">
            <div class="post-content-inner">
              
              If I also didn't pick up a Mamba last year I would be very interested in this mouse.  The adjustable nature of the mouse does scare me though.  I've found that the more something is adjustable the sooner it begins to feel old and loose.  I was glad to see that it takes an alan wrench to make those changes though.  Should help to keep the whole thing tight.  <BR><BR>I would love to see an Ars review or a comparison as was mentioned.  I know most people scoff at the thought of paying $100+ for a mouse, but since the first time I tried a Razer my eyes were opened.  I now have a Razer of some kind on every PC in the house.

              

              
              
            </div>
          </td>
        </tr>
        
    </table>
    
