        <tr>
          <td class="post-content">
            <div class="post-content-inner">
              
              Hmm, I've had an MX Revolution for about 3 or 4 years, and this is the first mouse since I got it that's gotten my attention.<BR><BR>Now, seeing the comments about the left handed users I guess I was lucky in my misery when I was a kid. My parents placed me in a very conservative Catholic school and, being left handed, the nuns would whack my hand hard with a ruler whenever they noticed me writing with my left hand. End result? Ambidexterity baby; I can use a mouse in either hand with no issues (though I do certain things such as holding a fork with the left hand only).

              

              
              
            </div>
          </td>
        </tr>
        
